CustomField.formula: IF( OR(LEN(ContactId)=0,LEN( AccountId)=0), 0,10) + IF( ISPICKVAL( Status ,""), 0,15) + IF( ISPICKVAL( Type ,""), 0,15) + IF( ISPICKVAL( Origin ,""), 0,15) + IF( ISPICKVAL( Reason ,""), 0,15) + IF(ISPICKVAL(Priority, ""),0,15) + IF(LEN( Subject )<5,0,15)
